From this experiment on, a multimeter is assumed to be necessary and will not be included in the required list of parts and materials.  In all subsequent illustrations, a digital multimeter will be shown instead of an analog meter unless there is some particular reason to use an analog meter.  You are encouraged to use \textit{both} types of meters to gain familiarity with the operation of each in these experiments.
 

