\section{ Potentiometer as a voltage divider}
\index{Experiment: Potentiometer as voltage divider}
 

\textbf{PARTS AND MATERIALS}
 

\begin{itemize}
\item Two 6-volt batteries
\item Carbon pencil "lead" for a mechanical-style pencil
\item Potentiometer, single turn, 5 k$\Omega$ to 50 k$\Omega$, linear taper (Radio Shack catalog \# 271-1714 through 271-1716)
