\textbf{INSTRUCTIONS}
 

 

"Ground" one lead of the detector to a metal object in contact with the earth (dirt).  Most any water pipe or faucet in a house will suffice.  Take the other lead and hold it close to an electrical appliance or lamp fixture.  \textbf{Do not try to make contact with the appliance or with any conductors within!}  Any AC electric fields produced by the appliance will be heard in the headphones as a buzzing tone.
 

