With R$_{1}$ and R$_{2}$ set equally to 5 k$\Omega$ in the simulation, it mimics the feedback potentiometer of the real circuit at mid-position (50\%).  To simulate the potentiometer at the 75\% position, set R$_{2}$ to 7.5 k$\Omega$ and R$_{1}$ to 2.5 k$\Omega$.
 


